text: The Cyprus Cup is a yearly women's association football tournament that has international teams from around the world. It takes place in the European country of Cyprus. The teams with the most titles are Canada and England, with 3 titles each. ==Results== Year Final Final Final Third Place Match Third Place Match Third Place Match Year Winner Score Runner-up 3rd Place Score 4th Place 2008 3–2 2–1 2009 3–1 1–1 aet 6–5 (pen.) 2010 1–0 4–0 2011 2–1 3–0 2012 2–0 3–1 2013 1–0 2–1 2014 2–0 1–1 aet 3–1 (pen.) 2015 1–0 3–2 ==Other websites== * * Cyprus Cup at RSSSF * Cyprus Cup on WomensSoccerUnited.com Category:Women's football
